FEV.DE.summary: FORTEC Elektronik AG provides industrial power supplies and display technologies in Germany and internationally. It operates in two segments, Data Visualisation Systems and Power Supplies. The Data Visualisation Systems segment offers standard kits and support services to product solutions developed in house and industrial monitors. The Power Supplies segment provides power supplies and DC/DC convertors. Fortec Elektronik AG was founded in 1984 and is based in Germering, Germany.
